##Yeah, I'm a mask guy

WMSYGSDR

Function introduction, each line has the earnest person, again the ordinary person also has the extraordinary story. Huazhong University of Science and Technology Press Official non-fiction story platform, the story of the people will meet here.

- In the event of an outbreak -

If they work overtime to produce one more piece, the people will have one less piece of panic caused by the shortage of face masks. If they produce one more piece, the pressure on government departments to fight the epidemic will be alleviated. If they produce one more piece, there will be a bridge between people to pass on guard and care.

”

1

As a clothing factory employee with only 79 employees, Xiao never imagined that one day people in their factory, from the boss to the employee, would hold such a high position in the eyes of relatives, friends, distant relatives and old neighbors until Feb. 8,2020.

Because, that day, their factory began to produce masks.

February 8, the boss in the employee group issued a notice, temporarily only 36 local machinists can, other employees back to work time and other notice. Originally, has been ready to resume work Xiaoyan, turned to continue to do the housework. The frustration of being ready for work and not being able to go to work didn't last long, and Xiao Yan's squad leader quickly called her up: "Come to work at 7:30 tomorrow and bring your own lunch. "

Making masks requires not only machinists, but also the auxiliaries of cutting thread and packing. Xiao Yan from the country is still waiting for the notice of a number of employees to take the lead in the professional identity of the mask auxiliary workers, out of the House, into his work unit.

This is Xiao Yan work for more than a decade, the most rigorous and the most complex of a resumption of work.

She must be prepared to resume work materials and personal trajectory documents. First of all, the ID card to the front of a good group of employees; second, in accordance with the guidance of personal trajectory proof method, their activities to the group of employees. The boss collects these two materials of good employee, hand them over to street enterprise to Resume Work Guidance Group unitedly subsequently. The Guidance Team will conduct the audit.

Fig. | One of the necessary materials for the resumption of work

Xiao doesn't understand what this material has to do with her returning to work. It wasn't until two days later, when two of her colleagues were persuaded to return home, that she knew what it meant.

Early the next morning, Xiao Yan with her husband to prepare their own lunch box, wear a mask before opening the door. She arrived at the factory before half past seven. Well, technically, it's at the factory door.

She was greeted by a colleague in a White Hazmat suit and a white surgical mask that revealed only her two black eyes. Usually warm and cheerful colleagues, see wearing a mask Xiao Yan walked to the front, the moment stiff up.

Xiao Yan thought it was a bit funny, but such a serious matter, she is not easy to joke about. Colleagues took her temperature, handed out masks and protective clothing, and instructed her to wash her hands and disinfect them before letting her into the factory. During the whole process, the two men talked no more than ten sentences. These processes also became the first step of Xiao Yan's next daily work when she came to the factory.

Xiao Yan felt mixed emotions as she dressed up and walked into her office. I don't know whether to be happy that the factory values the safety of ordinary workers, or nervous that the new pneumonia is not far from my life.

2

After entering the factory, the Monitor also explained that after the class is not allowed to gather and talk, not allowed to gather for lunch, no lunch break, no rest day, no leave, colleagues working from a distance, and other requirements. Not only did their colleagues keep their distance from each other in the workroom, but the mechanics did too.

Usually these women, where is the excitement to where to gather.

Xiao Yan listened to various requirements and matters needing attention, finally picked up the scissors and semi-finished mask. It's better to work than to stay, even if the conditions are so harsh. However, she was also a bit puzzled, just make a mask, really?

Before lunch, XIAO LEARNED THE IN & Out of the masks from her colleagues.

They don't make the masks. The government does. And their factory can return to work so early, is also the government's support.

Since the outbreak of new crown pneumonia, the mask has become a must for the entire Chinese people, will tuen items. Even now, there are few shops and pharmacies across China that can supply masks. Because there are only a limited number of producers upstream. Mask profit is not big, basically unprofitable, especially ordinary dust mask. Until now, the whole of China has been able to count this type of supplier.

The News of the face mask scramble is on the news from time to time; Mask Related Scams are commonplace; and even the latest way to show off one's wealth has gone from pork to a mask.

Xiao Yan knows, Xiao Yan's colleagues and Yang boss also know, but they never thought that this and their factory has anything to do with.

On the night of February 5th, Yang received a message from the street. That night, he made the decision to switch to full production of masks. Before this, what their factory does is the clothing processing business, does not have the mask production experience. And on top of that, we don't even have the ingredients for a mask.

Street feedback was quick, and when they got it, they started organizing teams to help organize the factors of production in the factory. On Feb. 6, the company began purchasing raw materials such as meltblown cloth and nose bar, as well as disinfection equipment, and provided a factory as a sterile workshop. February 7 training and trial production. On February 8th, the first 2,000 masks went off the shelves.

Melt blown cloth purchased by the government

Xiao Yan was assigned to the original factory. The day she arrived at the factory, all nine of the factory's mechanics were already skilled in the production of masks. Even though they were wearing hazmat suits that got in the way. Xiao Yan's job is to fix the masks made by the machinists one by one, then count them and pack them.

The 11 women had a clear division of labor and a clear mission.

3

All say "three women a play" , in the past workshop are the parents, West family gossip, but this will be the loudest is the sound of sewing machine. Everyone is like a new person, trying their best to do things, which has been very talkative Xiaoyan feel a little uncomfortable.

Every day in the workshop is filled with a sense of tension if there is no. This tension, in addition to security concerns, less talk, distance work, more because they have production targets.

When they do clothing, they are assembly line work, on-time delivery of the line, there is no requirement for production. Things are different now. Each mechanic has a daily production target of 500 to 600 masks, counting the output by number. Eleven people don't hold masks when they eat lunch or go to the bathroom, they hold them all the time.

At first, everyone's production method, or do clothing that set of processes flow pattern, one to do a process. But it soon became clear that the result was a total failure to meet production standards. In order to improve efficiency, the machinists quickly changed the production mode, regardless of the process, one person to make a complete mask.

The mechanic is making a mask

It worked so well that all nine of them met the quota that day. Together with the government-provided workshop, the two workshops can produce about 10,000 masks a day.

It took only two or three days for the plant to move from production to efficient operation.

More and more finished masks are piling up. More and more people know that Xiao Yan and his factory are producing masks. More and more people are coming to the house to recognize their relatives.

Everyone, from the boss to the employee, has people they don't know every day, asking for things and buying face masks, making connections, talking to each other. Many generous people, and even gave several times the market price to buy. As a low-cost labor-intensive small and medium-sized enterprise, the factory from the boss to the staff, has never enjoyed this kind of treatment.

Bosses have always had no say in the entrepreneurial world, and employees have always had little to show off among friends and relatives. But now, everywhere they go, they have a bunch of brothers and sisters, two-timing friends. Just say, "I make masks. ".

Xiao Yan had not yet gone to work when a variety of informed relatives came to book the mask. As an ordinary worker, surrounded by people all day long, it is inevitable that pride. But Pride is pride, and no matter how much friendship there is, a man who asks for a mask is always rejected. Not even your own mother or father.

It's not that they don't give face, it's that they have no right.

4

These masks are fully owned by the government. As the most urgent protection against the epidemic, the government is responsible for the unified dispatch and distribution. Every day or two, the government sends someone to pick it up.

Xiao Yan and her colleagues are a little proud to know that the masks they produce are anti-epidemic protective materials that the government distributes to ensure supply, stabilize the market and coordinate distribution. However, they were asked to promise to return to work after no leave, no lunch break, must complete the target and other harsh conditions. However, we still go to work on time every day, a loss of lunch to run to their posts. Xiao has never seen such enthusiasm and enthusiasm when making clothes.

Even if everyone's work enthusiasm is high, indicators are also very good, but Xiao Yan's two colleagues after work two days or was temporarily dismissed. It was not the work that was flawed, or the boss that was unforgiving, but the rework materials that they submitted were not up to scratch. Street re-work Guidance Group through the re-work materials submitted by them to verify that their household registration is not in the district, but the county below. On the same day, let their boss to persuade them to quit.

Although their activity trajectory is up to standard, production has been up to standard, there are no symptoms of fever and cold, and there are no new cases of coronary pneumonia in the home. But rules are rules. There's no bargaining.

Special period, can carry a rice bowl steadily all seem to be particularly not easy.

Xiao Yan's household registration is also county. But Luckily, her family has a house in the area, only five or six traffic lights away from the plant. Therefore, the conditions for the resumption of work.

The strict requirement of returning to work makes the colleagues who can stay in the factory cherish the opportunity they have. We do diligently mask, do not dare to have a trace of slack.

Not only do they dare not slacken off, but so do civil servants in government departments. The factory mask production work has just started to run well, February 11, a leader personally led to their factory, Inspection and inspection.

Xiao Yan worked in this factory for 3 years, seeing for the first time that a leader came to inspect their factory. When she mentioned it to her sister, she stressed it two or three times: "there are leaders to check it! "

While it is still far off for many companies to resume work, the local government has rushed to create conditions for their factories to resume work. It is clear to everyone that it is not how important their factories are or how big their bosses'face is, but how important this will be. Now, can produce mask smoothly, it is no longer the problem of economic efficiency, more like producing a can stabilize the heart of the people.

The leaders see peace of mind, the people of thousands of households see peace of mind.

Masks to be packed

5

No one cares what the profit margins are on masks, what the profit margins are on factories.
Everyone's eyes are looking at the same number: output.

At present, drug stores, shopping malls are out of stock, but the shortage is only temporary, some people are trying to create conditions to produce, some people are risking their lives to go out to produce.

Xiao Yan's sense of professional pride, is from the leadership to factory inspection, in the news posts to see their factory after the relevant news rising. Among her siblings, there are graduate and undergraduate students; there are technicians and civil servants, but she is not highly educated and has been engaged in manual labor. She rarely tells people about her job, but now she's happy to say, "yes, I'm a mask maker. "

As an employee of a low-cost labor-intensive enterprise, Xiao Yan does not have much advanced life realm. She and her colleagues had been working from 7:30 a.m. to 9 p.m. , selling their labor overtime in exchange for thousands of dollars a month. Even if I make a mask now, it's from 7:30 in the morning to 6:00 at night, and there's no day off. Such hard work is to earn more money, in order to better support the family.

Photo: colleagues

However, when she suddenly found that her factory to produce things, not only can bring material returns to them, but also with the whole country and people's lives closely related to the time, more or less a little sigh of emotion.

You can buy clothes, you can not buy clothes. And Right now, 1.4 billion people have to buy masks!

She had lived and worked in the city for three years and had never felt more connected to the people of the city than she did now.

"excited, " Xiao Yan thought, "a little bit. "

She thought, and her hand moved a little faster.

* Xiao Yan assumed an alias
